- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is a possible category as the paper analyzes the social dynamics of group buying behavior. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also a possible category as the paper discusses the role of personal benefit and social incentives in group buying behavior.
